<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Premium Motors | High Performance</title>
    <!-- Fonte Google para um visual mais agressivo/automotivo -->
    <link href="https://googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #d90429;
            --dark: #111;
            --light: #edf2f4;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #0b0b0b;
            color: var(--light);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Menu Moderno */
        nav {
            background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.95);
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        nav h1 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        nav div a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        nav div a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Hero Section com Parallax */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), 
                        url('https://unsplash.com');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-left: 10%;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .btn-main {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            width: fit-content;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .btn-main:hover {
            background: #ef233c;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(217, 4, 41, 0.4);
        }

        /* Cards Estilizados */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: -50px auto 50px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(30%);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .card:hover img {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .card-content h3 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        /* Animação */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #050505;
            border-top: 1px solid #222;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <h1>PREMIUM<span style="color:white">MOTORS</span></h1>
        <div>
            <a href="<html>.carros">Showroom</a>
            <a href="novidades.html">Novidades</a>
            <a href="sobre.html">Sobre</a>
            <a href="contato.html">Contato</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <h2>Poder & <br><span style="color: var(--primary)">Velocidade</span></h2>
        <p>Explore a curadoria mais exclusiva de supercarros e clássicos que definem gerações.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-main">Explorar Modelos</a>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="carros.jpeg" alt="Supercarro">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Performance Máxima</h3>
                <p>Onde a engenharia encontra a arte. Conheça os modelos que desafiam as leis da física.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="luxo.jpeg" alt="Luxo">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Design & Luxo</h3>
                <p>Interiores feitos à mão e acabamentos em fibra de carbono para o motorista exigente.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="cust.jpeg" alt="Custom">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Customização</h3>
                <p>Transforme sua máquina em uma peça única com nossos pacotes de personalização exclusiva.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Premium Motors. Design para entusiastas.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
